contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary}} '''EW''', '''Ew''', or '''ew''' may refer to: ==EW== * [[Each-way (bet)|Each-way]], a wager * East-West, used as a direction in scientific writing, comparable to NS for North-South or UD for Up-Down * [[Electrowinning]], an electro-chemical process * [[Equivalent weight]] in chemistry * [[eBaum's World]] * [[Eggplant Wizard]] * [[Electric Wizard]] * [[Electronic warfare]] * [[Entomological warfare]] * [[Emergency department|Emergency Ward]] of a hospital * [[Exawatt]], an SI unit of power * [[Extinct in the Wild]] an abbreviation for the conservation status level * ''[[Extreme Warfare]]'', a series of computer games * [[Electroweak]] interactions * [[Emma Watson]] ===Weekly publications=== * ''[[Entertainment Weekly]]'' magazine * ''[[Eugene Weekly]]'' newspaper ==Ew== * [[Ew (digraph)]], the digraph * ''"Eww"'', an [[interjection]] of disgust * [[Wikipedia:Edit war]] {{disambiguation}}
